        "accordion_item_rVBkwV": {
          "type": "accordion_item",
          "settings": {
            "title": "What causes dry mouth?",
            "content": "<div itemprop=\"text\">\n                        \n<p>Now that you know what it is, you might want to know what can cause dry mouth. As it turns out, there’s a <a href=\"/articles/blog/dry-mouth-causes-symptoms-solutions/\" data-uw-rm-brl=\"PR\" data-uw-original-href=\"/articles/blog/dry-mouth-causes-symptoms-solutions/\">long list of potential causes</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>Dehydration</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Stress</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Certain foods and drinks (especially those high in acidity, sugar, and caffeine, as well as alcohol)</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Menopause</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Aging</li>\n\n\n\n<li>The flu</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Medications (more than 400 prescription and over-the-counter medications have dry mouth as a known side effect)</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Diseases and medical conditions</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Nerve damage</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Radiation treatment (which can damage the salivary glands, leading to temporary or total saliva loss)</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Chemotherapy</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Smoking or chewing tobacco</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Recreational drug use</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Vaping</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<p>While it’s possible to experience dry mouth at any time, some people find they mostly have dry mouth overnight, which can interfere with sleep. When it comes to what causes dry mouth at night, there are a few additional reasons, such as:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>Breathing through the mouth while sleeping</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Use of a CPAP mask for sleep apnea</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Wearing dentures and retainers</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Sinusitis</li>\n\n\n\n<li>A deviated septum</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"swp-hidden-panel-wrap\" style=\"display: none; visibility: collapse; opacity: 0\"><div class=\"swp_social_panel swp_horizontal_panel swp_flat_fresh  swp_default_full_color swp_individual_full_color swp_other_full_color scale-100  scale-\" data-min-width=\"1100\" data-float-color=\"#ffffff\" data-float=\"none\" data-float-mobile=\"none\" data-transition=\"slide\" data-post-id=\"14206\">\n<div class=\"nc_tweetContainer swp_share_button swp_twitter\" data-network=\"twitter\"><a class=\"nc_tweet swp_share_link\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://twitter.com/intent/tweet?text=What+causes+dry+mouth%3F&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.smartmouth.com%2Ffaqs%2Fwhat-causes-dry-mouth%2F\" data-link=\"https://twitter.com/intent/tweet?text=What+causes+dry+mouth%3F&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.smartmouth.com%2Ffaqs%2Fwhat-causes-dry-mouth%2F\" data-uw-rm-brl=\"PR\" data-uw-original-href=\"https://twitter.com/intent/tweet?text=What+causes+dry+mouth%3F&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.smartmouth.com%2Ffaqs%2Fwhat-causes-dry-mouth%2F\" aria-label=\"twitter - open in a new tab\" data-uw-rm-empty-ctrl=\"\" data-uw-rm-ext-link=\"\" uw-rm-external-link-id=\"https://twitter.com/intent/tweet?text=what+causes+dry+mouth%3f&amp;url=https%3a%2f%2fwww.smartmouth.com%2ffaqs%2fwhat-causes-dry-mouth%2f$twitter\"><span class=\"swp_count swp_hide\"><span class=\"iconFiller\"><span class=\"spaceManWilly\"><i class=\"sw swp_twitter_icon\"></i><span class=\"swp_share\">Tweet</span></span></span></span></a></div>\n<div class=\"nc_tweetContainer swp_share_button swp_linkedin\" data-network=\"linkedin\"><a class=\"nc_tweet swp_share_link\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/cws/share?url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.smartmouth.com%2Ffaqs%2Fwhat-causes-dry-mouth%2F\" data-link=\"https://www.linkedin.com/cws/share?url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.smartmouth.com%2Ffaqs%2Fwhat-causes-dry-mouth%2F\" aria-label=\"linkedin - open in a new tab\" data-uw-rm-empty-ctrl=\"\" data-uw-rm-ext-link=\"\" uw-rm-external-link-id=\"https://www.linkedin.com/cws/share?url=https%3a%2f%2fwww.smartmouth.com%2ffaqs%2fwhat-causes-dry-mouth%2f$linkedin\"><span class=\"swp_count swp_hide\"><span class=\"iconFiller\"><span class=\"spaceManWilly\"><i class=\"sw swp_linkedin_icon\"></i><span class=\"swp_share\">Share</span></span></span></span></a></div>\n<div class=\"nc_tweetContainer swp_share_button swp_pinterest\" data-network=\"pinterest\"><a rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" class=\"nc_tweet swp_share_link noPop\" href=\"https://pinterest.com/pin/create/button/?url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.smartmouth.com%2Ffaqs%2Fwhat-causes-dry-mouth%2F\" onclick=\"event.preventDefault(); \n\t\t\t\t\t\t\tvar e=document.createElement('script');\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\te.setAttribute('type','text/javascript');\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\te.setAttribute('charset','UTF-8');\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\te.setAttribute('src','//assets.pinterest.com/js/pinmarklet.js?r='+Math.random()*99999999);\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\tdocument.body.appendChild(e);\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\" data-uw-rm-brl=\"PR\" data-uw-original-href=\"https://pinterest.com/pin/create/button/?url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.smartmouth.com%2Ffaqs%2Fwhat-causes-dry-mouth%2F\" aria-label=\"pinterest\" data-uw-rm-empty-ctrl=\"\"><span class=\"swp_count swp_hide\"><span class=\"iconFiller\"><span class=\"spaceManWilly\"><i class=\"sw swp_pinterest_icon\"></i><span class=\"swp_share\">Pin</span></span></span></span></a></div>\n<div class=\"nc_tweetContainer swp_share_button swp_facebook\" data-network=\"facebook\"><a class=\"nc_tweet swp_share_link\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.facebook.com/share.php?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.smartmouth.com%2Ffaqs%2Fwhat-causes-dry-mouth%2F\" data-link=\"https://www.facebook.com/share.php?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.smartmouth.com%2Ffaqs%2Fwhat-causes-dry-mouth%2F\" data-uw-rm-brl=\"PR\" data-uw-original-href=\"https://www.facebook.com/share.php?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.smartmouth.com%2Ffaqs%2Fwhat-causes-dry-mouth%2F\" aria-label=\"facebook - open in a new tab\" data-uw-rm-empty-ctrl=\"\" data-uw-rm-ext-link=\"\" uw-rm-external-link-id=\"https://www.facebook.com/share.php?u=https%3a%2f%2fwww.smartmouth.com%2ffaqs%2fwhat-causes-dry-mouth%2f$facebook\"><span class=\"swp_count swp_hide\"><span class=\"iconFiller\"><span class=\"spaceManWilly\"><i class=\"sw swp_faceb