        "accordion_item_wLHzgR": {
          "type": "accordion_item",
          "settings": {
            "title": "What is xerostomia?",
            "content": "<div itemprop=\"text\">\n                        \n<p>While you may be familiar with the terms “dry mouth” and “cottonmouth,” you could be a bit thrown by the word “xerostomia” — and you wouldn’t be alone. Although it sounds imposing, <a href=\"https://www.aaom.com/index.php%3Foption=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=107:xerostomia&amp;catid=22:patient-condition-information&amp;Itemid=120\" onclick=\"javascript:window.open('https://www.aaom.com/index.php%3Foption=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=107:xerostomia&amp;catid=22:patient-condition-information&amp;Itemid=120', '_blank', 'noopener'); return false;\" data-uw-rm-brl=\"PR\" data-uw-original-href=\"https://www.aaom.com/index.php%3Foption=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=107:xerostomia&amp;catid=22:patient-condition-information&amp;Itemid=120\">xerostomia</a> is simply the clinical term for dry mouth. When it comes to managing xerostomia, the same techniques you’d use for dry mouth apply.</p>\n<div class=\"swp-hidden-panel-wrap\" style=\"display: none; visibility: collapse; opacity: 0\"><div class=\"swp_social_panel swp_horizontal_panel swp_flat_fresh  swp_default_full_color swp_individual_full_color swp_other_full_color scale-100  scale-\" data-min-width=\"1100\" data-float-color=\"#ffffff\" data-float=\"none\" data-float-mobile=\"none\" data-transition=\"slide\" data-post-id=\"14208\">\n<div class=\"nc_tweetContainer swp_share_button swp_twitter\" data-network=\"twitter\"><a class=\"nc_tweet swp_share_link\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://twitter.com/intent/tweet?text=What+is+xerostomia%3F&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.smartmouth.com%2Ffaqs%2Fwhat-is-xerostomia%2F\" data-link=\"https://twitter.com/intent/tweet?text=What+is+xerostomia%3F&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.smartmouth.com%2Ffaqs%2Fwhat-is-xerostomia%2F\" data-uw-rm-brl=\"PR\" data-uw-original-href=\"https://twitter.com/intent/tweet?text=What+is+xerostomia%3F&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.smartmouth.com%2Ffaqs%2Fwhat-is-xerostomia%2F\" aria-label=\"twitter - open in a new tab\" data-uw-rm-empty-ctrl=\"\" data-uw-rm-ext-link=\"\" uw-rm-external-link-id=\"https://twitter.com/intent/tweet?text=what+is+xerostomia%3f&amp;url=https%3a%2f%2fwww.smartmouth.com%2ffaqs%2fwhat-is-xerostomia%2f$twitter\"><span class=\"swp_count swp_hide\"><span class=\"iconFiller\"><span class=\"spaceManWilly\"><i class=\"sw swp_twitter_icon\"></i><span class=\"swp_share\">Tweet</span></span></span></span></a></div>\n<div class=\"nc_tweetContainer swp_share_button swp_linkedin\" data-network=\"linkedin\"><a class=\"nc_tweet swp_share_link\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/cws/share?url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.smartmouth.com%2Ffaqs%2Fwhat-is-xerostomia%2F\" data-link=\"https://www.linkedin.com/cws/share?url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.smartmouth.com%2Ffaqs%2Fwhat-is-xerostomia%2F\" aria-label=\"linkedin - open in a new tab\" data-uw-rm-empty-ctrl=\"\" data-uw-rm-ext-link=\"\" uw-rm-external-link-id=\"https://www.linkedin.com/cws/share?url=https%3a%2f%2fwww.smartmouth.com%2ffaqs%2fwhat-is-xerostomia%2f$linkedin\"><span class=\"swp_count swp_hide\"><span class=\"iconFiller\"><span class=\"spaceManWilly\"><i class=\"sw swp_linkedin_icon\"></i><span class=\"swp_share\">Share</span></span></span></span></a></div>\n<div class=\"nc_tweetContainer swp_share_button swp_pinterest\" data-network=\"pinterest\"><a rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" class=\"nc_tweet swp_share_link noPop\" href=\"https://pinterest.com/pin/create/button/?url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.smartmouth.com%2Ffaqs%2Fwhat-is-xerostomia%2F\" onclick=\"event.preventDefault(); \n\t\t\t\t\t\t\tvar e=document.createElement('script');\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\te.setAttribute('type','text/javascript');\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\te.setAttribute('charset','UTF-8');\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\te.setAttribute('src','//assets.pinterest.com/js/pinmarklet.js?r='+Math.random()*99999999);\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\tdocument.body.appendChild(e);\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\" data-uw-rm-brl=\"PR\" data-uw-original-href=\"https://pinterest.com/pin/create/button/?url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.smartmouth.com%2Ffaqs%2Fwhat-is-xerostomia%2F\" aria-label=\"pinterest\" data-uw-rm-empty-ctrl=\"\"><span class=\"swp_count swp_hide\"><span class=\"iconFiller\"><span class=\"spaceManWilly\"><i class=\"sw swp_pinterest_icon\"></i><span class=\"swp_share\">Pin</span></span></span></span></a></div>\n<div class=\"nc_tweetContainer swp_share_button swp_facebook\" data-network=\"facebook\"><a class=\"nc_tweet swp_share_link\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.facebook.com/share.php?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.smartmouth.com%2Ffaqs%2Fwhat-is-xerostomia%2F\" data-link=\"https://www.facebook.com/share.php?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.smartmouth.com%2Ffaqs%2Fwhat-is-xerostomia%2F\" data-uw-rm-brl=\"PR\" data-uw-original-href=\"https://www.facebook.com/share.php?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.smartmouth.com%2Ffaqs%2Fwhat-is-xerostomia%2F\" aria-label=\"facebook - open in a new tab\" data-uw-rm-empty-ctrl=\"\" data-uw-rm-ext-link=\"\" uw-rm-external-link-id=\"https://www.facebook.com/share.php?u=https%3a%2f%2fwww.smartmouth.com%2ffaqs%2fwhat-is-xerostomia%2f$facebook\"><span class=\"swp_count swp_hide\"><span class=\"iconFiller\"><span class=\"spaceManWilly\"><i class=\"sw swp_facebook_icon\"></i><span class=\"swp_share\">Share</span></span></span></span></a></div>\n<div class=\"nc_tweetContainer swp_share_button total_shares total_sharesalt\"><span class=\"swp_count \">0 <span class=\"swp_label\">Shares</span></span></div>\n</div></div>\n<div class=\"swp-content-locator\"></div>                                            </div>"
